title: Star Wars Short Story Anthology Volume 1 (New Canon)
description:
This is the entire current collection of short stories published as apart of the new Star Wars expanded universe. 



1. "Blade Squadron" Part 1 & 2
-Star Wars Insider #149 & 150
Written by David J. Williams & Mark S. Williams

2. "One Thousand Levels Down"
- Star Wars Insider #151
Written by Alexander Freed

3. "The End of History"
- Star Wars Insider #154
Written by Alexander Freed

4. "Last Call at the Zero Angle"
- Star Wars Insider #156
Written by Jason Fry

5. "Orientation"
- Star Wars Insider #157
Written by John Jackson Miller
